OL,7,     Gbehind mankind's biggest
OL,8,     Gexperiment in particle physics.
OL,9,G2200FToo Near the Sun
OL,10,     GDocumentary exploring the race to
OL,11,     Gbuild the first thermonuclear
OL,12,     Gweapon. From 1966.
OL,13,G2250FA Very Peculiar Practice
OL,14,     GThe whole university seems to
OL,15,     Ghave succumbed to a sexually
OL,16,     Gtransmitted disease. Jock decides
OL,17,     Gthey must trace the source of the
OL,18,     Goutbreak. Contains adult humour.
